reviews.text: Authentic Arabic food with great taste, no surprise though. And great service too!
Really amazing hummus and falafel! Quite expensive, but recommend it. Very friendly people, as well.

Delicious Arabic food in Hong Kong side Wanchai station ! Owner is very nice chef of the restaurant is doing great job to make amazing food. Hummus and Arabic shawarma is so delicious.. highly recommend for locals and tourist to must try this place .
It was a tasty and authentic Lebanese meal, but man eye watering expensive $$$$$. Small pickles, Homous, two arabic bread and 3 falafels ...come to $66 😬
Nice food in a small flat on a commercial building. Better book in advance as only limited seats available.
